# Render production — Gmail SMTP is blocked on free tier; use Brevo (HTTPS)
# 1. Sign up at https://www.brevo.com
# 2. app.brevo.com → Senders & IP → Add sender → verify your Gmail (click link in inbox)
# 3. app.brevo.com → SMTP & API → API keys tab → Generate (NOT the SMTP keys tab)
#    API keys start with xkeysib- — SMTP keys (xsmtpsib-) will NOT work
# 4. Add to Render → Environment:
BREVO_API_KEY=
EMAIL_USER=gopassdorsu@gmail.com
